<h1>DownloadPlusPlus</h1>
<hr size="1" width="100%" color="black">
<pre class="prettyprint">rpm install DownloadPlusPlus</pre>
<hr size="1" width="100%" color="black">
DownloadPlusPlus is a ReCT Package that adds a more advanced Downloader.
The main difference is that its async and provides download Progress
<pre class="prettyprint">
package sys; use sys;
package dll DownloadPlusPlus; use DownloadPlusPlus;
var dpp <- make Downloader("url/to/file", "outputFile.txt");
dpp->Start();

while(!dpp->Complete)
{
  Print("Progress: " + string(dpp->Progress) + "%");
}

Print(Download done!);
</pre>
<hr size="1" width="100%" color="black">
